583
00:23:24,940 --> 00:23:26,780
My sister-in-law has a new lover.

584
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:28,100
That new lover

585
00:23:28,100 --> 00:23:29,540
has quite a bit of wealth.

586
00:23:29,700 --> 00:23:31,780
So, my brother felt inferior

587
00:23:31,940 --> 00:23:33,300
and didn't even try to stop her.

588
00:23:33,300 --> 00:23:34,980
He even helped her move

589
00:23:34,980 --> 00:23:37,020
to be with her new love.

590
00:23:37,220 --> 00:23:39,060
He told me this when he was drunk.

591
00:23:39,060 --> 00:23:40,660
I wouldn't dare tell my parents,

592
00:23:40,660 --> 00:23:42,180
or he'd get beaten again.

593
00:23:51,260 --> 00:23:53,100
You must have something on your mind,

594
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:54,900
which is why you're asking me

595
00:23:54,900 --> 00:23:56,900
if I've ever deceived my family.

596
00:23:58,020 --> 00:23:59,940
If you want to talk, I'm your tree hole.

597
00:23:59,940 --> 00:24:00,980
If you don't want to talk,

598
00:24:00,980 --> 00:24:02,040
I'm still your tree hole.

599
00:24:09,980 --> 00:24:11,020
I have

600
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:13,380
a trusted elder,

601
00:24:14,500 --> 00:24:15,940
but I suddenly realized

602
00:24:16,060 --> 00:24:18,060
that he seems
to be hiding something from me.

603
00:24:18,340 --> 00:24:19,300
And I'm also

604
00:24:20,580 --> 00:24:22,340
hiding many things from him.

605
00:24:22,980 --> 00:24:24,300
I don't know why that elder

606
00:24:24,300 --> 00:24:25,740
is doing this.

607
00:24:26,540 --> 00:24:28,260
But I know you're kind.

608
00:24:28,500 --> 00:24:30,140
You wouldn't hurt others.

609
