and relatives in Yong'an.

707
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:48,620
Your sixth brother...

708
00:29:49,780 --> 00:29:51,060
Prince Zhao?

709
00:29:52,660 --> 00:29:54,940
He's always had connections
with the court

710
00:29:55,700 --> 00:29:57,420
and even recommended officials?

711
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:06,940
These are all bestowed by the Princess.

712
00:30:06,940 --> 00:30:08,420
