She said

713
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:09,940
these fish badges

714
00:30:09,940 --> 00:30:12,420
will be your entrance permit.

715
00:30:12,420 --> 00:30:13,740
You'll be able to enter and leave

716
00:30:13,740 --> 00:30:15,300
the Princess's mansion freely.

717
00:30:16,340 --> 00:30:17,540
Thanks for her kindness,

718
00:30:17,740 --> 00:30:19,580
but I can go back on my own.

719
00:30:19,740 --> 00:30:20,740
Mr. Lin,

720
00:30:20,740 --> 00:30:22,460
please understand us.

721
00:30:22,740 --> 00:30:24,540
These are the orders of the Princess.

722
00:30:24,860 --> 00:30:26,420
Please get in the carriage.

723
00:31:06,660 --> 00:31:08,940
You're not yet 30, right?

724
00:31:08,940 --> 00:31:10,220
So young,

725
00:31:10,220 --> 00:31:11,820
yet already the Vice Prefect.

726
00:31:12,180 --> 00:31:14,300
This is truly a mark of great promise.

727
00:31:14,580 --> 00:31:15,980
You're upright,

728
00:31:15,980 --> 00:31:17,140
handsome,

729
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:18,100
and elegant.

730
00:31:18,540 --> 00:31:21,140
The Princess appreciates
those qualities the most.

731
00:31:21,580 --> 00:31:24,020
The Princess has invited you
several times before,

732
00:31:24,180 --> 00:31:26,060
showing great favor.

733
00:31:26,820 --> 00:31:28,540
If you're willing,

734
00:31:29,060 --> 00:31:31,860
you can even become
one of the Three Lords.

735
00:31:35,540 --> 00:31:37,900
(Yunshui Manor)

736
00:31:39,660 --> 00:31:40,620
Mr. Lin.

737
00:31:44,260 --> 00:31:45,220
Mr. Lin,

738
00:31:45,460 --> 00:31:46,310
please consider

739
00:31:46,320 --> 00:31:47,860
what I said.

740
00:31:47,860 --> 00:31:49,860
After all,
it's the wish of the Princess.

741
00:31:50,180 --> 00:31:51,460
With the Princess's support

742
00:31:51,460 --> 00:31:52,660
and your character,

743
00:31:52,660 --> 00:31:54,020
you'll have a bright future.

744
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:55,660
You flatter me.

745
00:31:55,780 --> 00:31:56,740
You flatter me.

746
00:31:57,620 --> 00:31:58,660
Mr. Lin, goodbye.

747
00:32:01,340 --> 00:32:03,100
Grandpa, I don't understand

748
00:32:03,100 --> 00:32:04,700
what they're saying at all.

749
00:32:04,900 --> 00:32:05,860
Let's go.

750
00:32:05,860 --> 00:32:06,720
Let's go to the diner.

751
00:32:06,760 --> 00:32:08,040
Something big is going to happen.

752
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:09,100
- Hurry.
- What's wrong?

753
00:32:09,110 --> 00:32:09,760
Hurry, hurry up.

754
00:32:09,780 --> 00:32:12,100
(Temporarily Closed)
Handsome, Handsome.

755
00:32:12,100 --> 00:32:13,660
Don't be so quiet inside.

756
00:32:13,660 --> 00:32:15,140
Come out and let us see you.

757
00:32:15,140 --> 00:32:17,320
Handsome, let us see if you're okay,

758
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:19,020
(Handsome Shen's Sayings)
and we'll leave.

759
00:32:19,020 --> 00:32:20,940
- Handsome.
- Handsome.

760
00:32:21,100 --> 00:32:22,420
- Handsome.
- Handsome.

761
00:32:22,420 --> 00:32:23,660
Come out and meet us.

762
00:32:24,300 --> 00:32:26,020
Are all the women in ancient times

763
00:32:26,020 --> 00:32:27,340
so crazy?

764
00:32:28,940 --> 00:32:29,780
Deyuan,

765
00:32:29,780 --> 00:32:30,780
hang in there.

766
00:32:32,740 --> 00:32:33,580
What to do?

767
00:32:33,580 --> 00:32:34,540
Come on.

768
00:32:34,820 --> 00:32:36,340
This is too crazy.

769
00:32:41,260 --> 00:32:42,220
Come on.

