795
00:33:26,020 --> 00:33:27,300
I will definitely manage

796
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:28,220
my Gongcai Fan.

797
00:33:28,220 --> 00:33:29,740
Gongcai Fan?

798
00:33:29,740 --> 00:33:30,660
Let me warn you:

799
00:33:30,660 --> 00:33:31,620
Shen Shaojie,

800
00:33:31,860 --> 00:33:33,220
the one these women like

801
