817
00:33:56,820 --> 00:33:58,060
Just give it a rest.

818
00:33:58,060 --> 00:33:59,280
You don't look like an idol,

819
00:33:59,280 --> 00:34:00,940
but you've already got
the idol's burden.

820
00:34:00,940 --> 00:34:02,340
I thought you might get better,

821
00:34:02,340 --> 00:34:03,580
but instead, you've regressed.

822
00:34:03,700 --> 00:34:05,380
What do you mean by this?

823
00:34:07,060 --> 00:34:08,140
You're all here.

824
00:34:09,100 --> 00:34:10,240
Something big has happened.

825
00:34:10,500 --> 00:34:11,740
You simply can't believe it.

826
00:34:14,860 --> 00:34:16,340
Why are there so many people in front?

827
00:34:16,340 --> 00:34:17,620
Why is the shop closed?

828
00:34:17,620 --> 00:34:19,020
Are we not doing business anymore?

829
00:34:19,020 --> 00:34:21,300
It's all because of Shen Gongcai's fans.

830
00:34:23,140 --> 00:34:24,420
They're all his fans?

831
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:26,060
What about mine?

832
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:27,500
Dad, get to the point.

833
00:34:28,500 --> 00:34:29,460
Yes, yes.

834
00:34:29,700 --> 00:34:30,780
Yangyang and I

835
00:34:30,780 --> 00:34:32,540
just saw

836
00:34:32,700 --> 00:34:34,300
that the Princess's servants

837
00:34:34,300 --> 00:34:35,660
sent Mr. Lin

838
00:34:35,660 --> 00:34:36,700
back to his mansion.

839
00:34:36,700 --> 00:34:38,100
From what we overheard,

840
00:34:38,220 --> 00:34:41,220
