(Shaoguang's Food Notes)

911
00:37:07,820 --> 00:37:13,060
(Xuanwei Ham:
Yunnan Xuanwei Ham as fillings)

912
00:37:13,060 --> 00:37:18,300
(This mooncake
is both savory and sweet.)

913
00:37:49,210 --> 00:37:52,540
Wear a sunset glow upon the brow

914
00:37:52,540 --> 00:37:55,800
Breeze sways,
wind chimes hang below the cloud

915
00:37:56,120 --> 00:37:59,140
Hear one chime ring,
tugging at the heart

916
00:37:59,140 --> 00:38:02,240
True feelings perhaps
can only be sensed

917
00:38:02,820 --> 00:38:06,250
Misty is you, clear is you

918
00:38:06,250 --> 00:38:09,670
Seeking stars in fog,
seeing your shadow under the moon

919
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:13,060
Words held back, feelings unrestrained

920
00:38:13,060 --> 00:38:18,210
Could the road ahead,
let us gaze but not doubt

921
00:38:20,170 --> 00:38:23,310
Mistook all eyes see as cold ice

922
00:38:23,310 --> 00:38:26,710
Yet let dusk dye
the ears and temples red

923
00:38:26,950 --> 00:38:30,010
Even holding breath
couldn't help but stop

924
00:38:30,010 --> 00:38:33,060
Exposing my warmed heart held tight

925
00:38:33,650 --> 00:38:37,110
Bustling is you, desolate is you

926
00:38:37,110 --> 00:38:40,490
Reservedly drawing you into this life

927
00:38:40,490 --> 00:38:43,920
Hesitating, undecided,
the heart hard to deceive

928
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:49,740
Worldly rules and taboos,
how could they make me give up

929
00:38:49,980 --> 00:38:54,350
When rushing to you,
leaving my deep thoughts in disarray

930
00:38:54,350 --> 00:38:56,620
I still foolishly see it
as a good time

931
00:38:56,620 --> 00:39:00,940
Heart stirs,
wind swirls the lightest ripples

932
00:39:00,940 --> 00:39:03,710
A thousand tangled thoughts concealed

933
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:07,990
Saved a whole lifetime,
hastening to you, urgent over miles

934
00:39:07,990 --> 00:39:11,430
To make the wandering heart
return home henceforth

935
00:39:11,430 --> 00:39:14,870
To draw near what seems beyond reach

936
00:39:14,870 --> 00:39:19,720
Through life and death changes,
only we never cease, never yield

937
00:39:19,720 --> 00:39:24,440
Perhaps affection barely passes muster

938
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:26,610
But love forever

939
00:39:26,620 --> 00:39:32,380
Will make up for our mutual care,
mutual bond

940
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:37,200
Saved a whole lifetime,
hastening to you, urgent over miles

941
00:39:37,200 --> 00:39:40,560
To make the wandering heart
return home from now

942
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:44,030
To dare approach
what seems beyond reach

943
00:39:44,030 --> 00:39:45,770
Through life and death changes

944
00:39:45,770 --> 00:39:52,130
Only you, never cease, never yield

